      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know, but it's not just about the work. it's the constant pressure, the feeling that i'm always failing, and the sheer exhaustion of having to wake up and pretend i'm okay every single day. it feels like i'm just drowning in slow motion. there's no point in trying to \"heal\" when the whole foundation is gone. it just feels like a cycle that never ends.",
