      "content": "it's just... there's no end in sight. even if i get help, i'm still the same person, facing the same empty lab, the same lost years. i'm just so tired of fighting a losing battle. sometimes i look at everything and think, why bother even trying to fix something that's already fundamentally broken? it feels like the only way to actually find some peace is to just stop everything. to just let go.",
