      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just that \"help\" always feels like more work. more talking, more explaining, more pretending. and even if i do, i'm still stuck in this life that feels like a mistake. i just look at the concept of peace, of actually being able to rest without the guilt or the constant noise in my head, and it feels like that's only possible when everything just... stops. like, if the struggle is gone, then the person is gone too. does that make any sense?",
